Hi, everyone! I'm a senior content marketing manager at Carta (previously an early employee at Credit Karma and Funding Circle). You can read more about how I ended up in the content world on <https://www.linkedin.com/in/jenna-lee-79bb9b38/|LinkedIn>. It involves my English-teacher mom and punishment essays.

In my spare time, I bake, play music, freelance (mortgages in the Bay Area are ridiculous :upside_down_face:), and run an Instagram account for my <https://www.instagram.com/iamsqueaks/|cat> (I'm not crazy, I swear). Excited to learn from all of you!
